Scan a host or network to detect hardware.

Usage:
  cani scan HOST [flags]

Flags:
  -h, --help              help for scan
  -H, --host string       Host or IP of the BMC
  -k, --insecure          Do not enforce certificate validation (default true)
  -P, --password string   Password for the BMC
  -p, --port int          Port number for the BMC (default 443)
  -U, --username string   Username for the BMC (default "admin")

Global Flags:
      --config string   Path to the configuration file
  -D, --debug           additional debug output
  -S, --simulation      Use simulation mode for hsm-simulation-environment
